{
  "stem": "7832.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in that camp as reserves for the gas chamber, for the crematorium, because they were-- they were burning two men and one woman, because that was the best efficient thing to have the crematorium work efficiently.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the woman has a little more flesh on the body, because of her breasts, and the men don't.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were using two men and one-- two men and one woman for the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were reserved, is what we were told by our block [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because every time we asked for some food or rations, you think you're here to live?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You are here to be a reserve for-- for the-- for that chimney.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's when we found out what that chimney was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We saw the flames and the smoke and the stench was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't know what it was for a few days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, your parents are in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Your siblings are burned there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's what that-- and oh, my God, after that, for sure, more people wanted to die.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and so every day, the selections were for different purposes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took us, a lot of us, for the gas chamber, for that third person so the crematorium burns better.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a lot of us were lucky enough to be selected for work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was selected for experiments. 15 of us, one morning, were selected.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had to undress outside, and we had-- and-- and this doctor, this German doctor examined our body.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And with they were-- they took us out because we had no blemished bodies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They wanted-- they wanted people with smooth skin and no blemishes on the skin.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
